com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.datastore.id.gen

Interface ItemIdGenerationStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RandomItemIdGenerationStrategy, SequentialItemIdGenerationStrategy, SingleItemIdGenerationStrategy

    public interface ItemIdGenerationStrategy
    Determines an algorithm on how to generate a valid SNOMED CT Item identifier without extension namespace-identifier, partition-identifier and check-digit parts.
    Since:
    4.0

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static ItemIdGenerationStrategy RANDOM
      ItemIdGenerationStrategy implementation which generates a random Item identifier, independent of the given namespace and category.
